WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.917
Myocarditis is inflammation of the myocardium, most

00:00:02.917 --> 00:00:05.000
often triggered by viral infection.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.917
Annual incidence is estimated at up to

00:00:07.917 --> 00:00:10.000
twenty-two per one hundred thousand.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.917
It presents across all adult ages, with

00:00:12.917 --> 00:00:15.000
male predominance in viral cases.
